snippet.title: Christmas Stories with Diana and Roma | 1 Hour Video
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma in the Best Christmas Stories for Kids. 
This Christmas video is filled with festive fun and will make your Christmas season truly magical!

0:32:39 Oliver Becomes a Wizard Story
0:36:28 The Gingerbread Man House Story
0:40:04 Decorate the Christmas Tree with Friends
0:46:36 Diana and Roma Help mom and decorate the Christmas tree

1:00:30 New Baby Brother for Christmas
